issue.title: Form data in the request body of a custom request settings in any form not sending data
issue.body:
Hello @zhouyanliang it seems its only the initial image that you pushed out to introduce this feature that is working as it is supposed to. All others are not for me.

Associated fields relationship ie one to many (most especially), many to one does not get fired with the data in a webhook for example.

I was having this issue until i reverted back to that image of the 18th October 2023 that introduced this feature and resolved this attached discussion.

Please look into this.


_Originally posted by @zhouyanliang in https://github.com/nocobase/nocobase/discussions/1933#discussioncomment-7282935_

comment.body: Yes, basically this plus other info within the table that is supposed to come with it - but basically that's the format that it comes in with the image that is working.

issue.title: Form data in the request body of a custom request settings in any form not sending data
issue.body:
Hello @zhouyanliang it seems its only the initial image that you pushed out to introduce this feature that is working as it is supposed to. All others are not for me.

Associated fields relationship ie one to many (most especially), many to one does not get fired with the data in a webhook for example.

I was having this issue until i reverted back to that image of the 18th October 2023 that introduced this feature and resolved this attached discussion.

Please look into this.


_Originally posted by @zhouyanliang in https://github.com/nocobase/nocobase/discussions/1933#discussioncomment-7282935_

comment.body:
Yes it is only the nomitemid data - which is an associated table (1 to many) to the nominations table that the data doesn't come with the webhook when it is fired.

For further context, the nomitemid data is an Array that is supposed to come with all the Item IDs and their information in the table below:
![image](https://github.com/nocobase/nocobase/assets/147355081/f2996769-7ab0-4a1c-892a-d7e99283c2fd)
